Geo-Aware LLM Request Routing Is Available in the Einstein Generative AI Platform

The Einstein generative AI platform now routes large language model (LLM) requests to the servers that are closest to where your Einstein generative AI platform instance is located. Geo-aware routing includes LLM API requests made by Einstein generative AI features that use the Einstein generative AI platform. If a model isnâ€™t available in a nearby region, the requests are routed to the US.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with an Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on.

When: Geo-aware LLM request routing is available starting in July 2024.
title: Geo-Aware LLM Request Routing Released
